data.title: University of Illinois College of Medicine
data.text:
Dr. Maureen Chavez is originally from the Philippines. She earned her undergraduate degree in biology at University of Houston Clear Lake before going on to earn her medical degree from University of the East/Ramon Magsaysay Memorial Medical Center College of Medicine. Maureen completed her pediatric residency at University of Texas Medical Branch.

In her free time Maureen enjoys traveling, cooking, dancing, reading, listening to music, and DIY-projects.
